      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija us winnu:\nDabbn man weennu treju Gaddu\nGochtinu/ un weenit Kasu no trim\nGaddeem / un weenut Aunu no\ntrim Gaddeem/ un weenu Uhbeli/\nun weenn jaunn Ballodi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch dabbnija tam\nſcho wiſſu/ un wiꞥſch dallija tohs\nwiddu puſcham / un likke ikkatru\nDaktu ween prettohtru / bet tohs\nPutnus ne dallija wiꞥſch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Maitas Putni no-\nlaidahs us tahm/ un Ahbrams no-\ndsinne tohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad ta Saute nogah-\nje / tad kritte zeets Meegs us Ah-\nbramu / un reds Istruhzinaſcha-\nna/ un teela Tumfiba kritte pahr\nwinnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija us Ah-\nbram: Scho finui teefcham/ ka\ntaws Dsimnums fwesch buhs\nkahdâ Semmê / kas tam ne pee-\nderr/ un tee kalpohs winneem/ un\nwinxi teem gruhti darrihs tſchetr-\ntints Gaddus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tomehr es arridsan foḣdi-\nfchu to Tantu/ kam tee kalpohs/ un\npehz to iſees tee ar leelu Mantu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tu ceſi pee taweem Teh-\nweem ar Meeru / (un) tapti ap-\nrafts labbâ Wezzuma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas zettorta Muhscha\nAugums nahks atkaſ schai Wee-\ntâ / jo ta Ahmoriteru Metaifniba\nirr lihds fchin wehl ne peepildita.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notikte / kad ta\nSaule nogahje un Tumfiba met-\ntahs / tad redſt / tur bija weens\nduhmains Zeplis / un weena Ug-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "guns Leeſma / kas zaue ſchee\nDalteem zaue gahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tanni Deenâ darrija ta\nKUNGS Detribu ar Ahbramu\nfazzidams : Tawam Dsimmu\nman eſmu es fcho Semini dewis\nno tahs Egiptes Uppes / lihds ta\nleelai Uppei Wrat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tohs Keniterus/un tohs K\nnisiterus/ un tohs Kadmoniterus\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tohs Eetiterus / un toh\nWereſiterus/ un tohs Rewaim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tohs Ahmoriterus / u\ntohs Kananiterus / un tohs Gi\ngositerus/ un tohs Jebusiterus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XVI. Nodalla.\nSara dohd Ahbramam ſawu Kalponi Ahga\npar Seewu : 1. Ta tohp gruhta : 4.\nbehg nohſt no fawas Gaspaschas : 7. Bet\nta Engeta Pawehlefchanu ta atgreeschahs a\npakat : 8. Tas apjohla winnai ſawa Dſi\nmuma Wairoſchana : 10. Dsemde Jſmâêfu : 1\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "NSarâiAhbramia Se\nwa ne dsemdeja tam r\nneeka/ un tai bija ween\nEgipteruKalponeAhgareWahrd\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sarât fazzija uhs A\nbramu:Rangi jelle/tasKUNGS\nirr mann atſtlehdſis / ka es t\ndsemdeju / eij jelle pee mann\nKalpones/ iaſchu es zaue winna\napbehrnota tapſchu/unAhbram\nklansija Sarajas Balsi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad rehme Sarâi Ahbram\nSeewa to Ahgari ſawu Egipter\nKalponi/ pehz definitis Gaddeem\nkad Ahbrams eekſch tahsSemine\nKanaân bij dſihwojts/ un dewe t\nAhbramam ſawani Wihran pa\nSeewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch gahje pee Ahga\n"
    }
  ],
